ww.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=5792&amp;awinaffid=531979&amp;clickref=1-1-2351415-1-0-0&amp;ued=https://www.musicmagpie.co.uk/store/products/apple-macbook-air-apple-m1-3-2-13-2020-8gb-256gb-grey\" target=\"_blank\">£616.99 or £22.40 per month</a> (19.9% APR finance) over 36 months.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the biggest names on this list, MusicMagpie lets you buy (and sell) all kinds of tech and even, as the name suggests, CDs and vinyl. Mac buyers may find this lack of specialisation worrying.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><table><thead><tr><th>Pros</th><th>Cons</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Options to buy, rent and finance a Mac</td><td>Limited purchase and technical support</td></tr><tr><td>Up to 36 months interest-bearing finance available</td><td>No more than 12-month warranty available</td></tr><tr><td>Fast delivery</td><td>Not Apple specialists</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Unknown capability or certification of technicians</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Apple Refurbished</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Apple Refurbished home page\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1663w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-refurbished-homepage.png?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenth